  <h1>No hassle. Low cost. That's the beauty of travel insurance from World First.</h1>
  <p>Heading off? Don't go without us. We are the <a href="/home/travel-insurance/destinations.aspx">worldwide travel insurance specialists</a> and have 40 years of experience providing <a href="/home/travel-insurance.aspx">holiday insurance cover</a> for all kinds of people, going to all kinds of places and doing all kinds of wonderful things. We offer a range of policies for single trip, long stay and multi-trip insurance as well as <a href="/home/travel-insurance/annual-multi-trip.aspx">cheap annual travel insurance</a> if you travel frequently. We also provide exceptional value <a href="/home/travel-insurance/medical-problems.aspx">medical travel insurance</a> and often find we are able to offer cover to people with medical conditions who have been refused cover elsewhere.</p>
  <h2>A choice of cover for families, sports and business</h2>
  <p>We offer a range of policies with different levels of cover for all kinds of travellers. So, if you are looking for a <a href="/home/travel-insurance/families.aspx">family travel insurance quote</a>, cover for a business trip, gap year or extreme sports, we can help. All policies include free cover for over 150 sports and activities, as well as luggage and money, travel delay, personal liability and legal costs. Emergency medical cover is included too, with cover starting at &pound;1m and rising to &pound;10m with our Superior policy.</p>
  <h2>Insurance that's tailored to you and your trip</h2>
  <p>However you like to travel, we have a policy that is right for you. Talk to our <a href="/home/contact-us.aspx">specialist travel insurance team</a> and tell them all about it! They can talk to you about insurance for <a href="/home/travel-insurance/medical-problems/medical-screening.aspx">pre-existing medical conditions</a> or <a href="/home/travel-insurance/seniors/over-65s.aspx">over 65 travel insurance</a> as well as cruise travel insurance, golf travel insurance and winter sports travel insurance - and even wedding cover if you plan on getting hitched abroad. They will be able to give you instant <a href="/home/travel-insurance.aspx">travel insurance quotes</a> too, and can arrange cover straight away if you need it. You'll also benefit from a 14 day money back guarantee on any policy.</p>
  <p>To find out more, just give us a call on <strong>0345 90 80 161</strong> or get an instant quote.</p>
  <p>We'll take care of the rest.</p>
  
